[32m│[0m   - `success`: boolean indicating if operation succeeded                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `message`: descriptive message about the result                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `redirect`: URL to redirect to (usually "/")                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 3. **POST /delete_url/<id>**                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Description**: Endpoint for deleting saved URLs                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Authentication**: Not required                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Parameters**: URL path parameter `id` (numeric ID of URL to delete)      [32m│[0m
