[32m│[0m actual ID)                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Response**: Redirects to homepage                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## Authentication Requirements                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **No authentication required** for any discovered endpoints. The application [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m is completely open with:                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No login/logout endpoints found                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No session cookies required for operations                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All endpoints accessible without authentication                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
